entries.description: Add support for getUrl operation. The API can be used to generate a URL that represents an object in Amazon S3. The url can only be used to download the object content if the object has public read permissions. Original issue: https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-java-v2/issues/860

entries.category: Amazon Elastic Container Service for Kubernetes
entries.description: Added support to control private/public access to the Kubernetes API-server endpoint
Adds the Java vendor the user agent as well as using the updated user agent for all HTTP calls
Only set content type of S3 `CreateMultipartUploadRequest` if `Content-Type` header is not present and honor the overridden content type.
AWS Config adds a new API called SelectResourceConfig to run advanced queries based on resource configuration properties.
